data.description: Welcome to this luxurious 5-bedroom fully furnished townhome END UNIT, located in the Championsgate Golf Club community. This property boasts elegant decor, impeccable condition, and 5 spacious bedrooms with 4 bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of sophistication and comfort. Step into your own Private Pool with lake view, providing a serene space for relaxation and enjoyment. Big Plus, NO REARS NEIGHBORS which allows for privacy while enjoying pool time with family and friends!     Residents of Championsgate Golf Club have exclusive access to an impressive range of amenities, including golf courses, tennis courts, community-wide shuttle service, entertainment complexes, in-house concierge services, restaurants, bars, a lazy river, water slides, a video arcade, a fitness center, and 24-hour security. The location is also conveniently situated near shopping centers, Championsgate City Center, Reunion Resort, and top golf courses. Additionally, it offers excellent proximity to popular attractions such as Walt Disney World and Universal Orlando.    Don't miss out on the chance to own this exquisite townhome, ideal for both vacationing and investment purposes. Schedule your showing today and experience the epitome of resort-style living!    The house will NOT BE available for showing during May.
